rime_numbers" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Prime numbers">prime numbers</=
a>. The dark diagonal lines in the spiral hint at the hypothesized approxim=
ate <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Independence_(probability_theo=
ry)" title=3D"Independence (probability theory)">independence</a> between b=
