own as <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ulam_spiral#Hardy_and_Littl=
ewood's_Conjecture_F" title=3D"Ulam spiral">Hardy and Littlewood's Conjectu=
re F</a>.</figcaption></figure>
