-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:3.836ex; height:2.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \Om=
ega ^{-}.}"></span> In both cases, the equations of the theories had unexpl=
ained solutions, which led to conjecture of the existence of an unknown <a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Particle" title=3D"Particle">particle=
</a>, and the search for these particles. In both cases, these particles we=
re discovered a few years later by specific experiments.<sup id=3D"cite_ref=
-borel_134-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/=
Mathematics#cite_note-borel-134"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>131<s=
pan class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-135" class=
=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematics#cite_no=
