">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-136" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D=
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematics#cite_note-136"><span class=3D"ci=
te-bracket">[</span>133<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Specific_sciences">Specific=
 sciences</h3></div>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id=3D"Physics">Physics</h4></div>
<link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r=
1320445320"><div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">=
Main article: <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Relationship_between=
_mathematics_and_physics" title=3D"Relationship between mathematics and phy=
sics">Relationship between mathematics and physics</a></div>
<figure class=3D"mw-default-size" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
