=3D"300"></a><figcaption>The skin of this <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.o=
rg/wiki/Giant_pufferfish" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Giant pufferfish">=
giant pufferfish</a> exhibits a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tu=
ring_pattern" title=3D"Turing pattern">Turing pattern</a>, which can be mod=
eled by <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reaction%E2%80%93diffusion=
