racket">]</span></a></sup> Similarly, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w=
iki/Meteorology" title=3D"Meteorology">meteorology</a>, <a href=3D"https://=
en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oceanography" title=3D"Oceanography">oceanography</a>=
, and <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Planetology" class=3D"mw-red=
irect" title=3D"Planetology">planetology</a> also use mathematics due to th=
